        <item>
            <title>全新入门版 Apple Pencil (USB-C) 登场　USB-C 充电不支援压力感应</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/apple-introduces-new-apple-pencil/notebook/ipad-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-introduces-new-apple-pencil</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/17/apple-introduces-new-apple-pencil/notebook/ipad-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 14:25:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Pencil]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199849</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>之前一直谣传今晚 Apple 会推出新 iPad，想不到竟然原来是新的 Apple Pencil。今次推出的并非取代现有 Apple Pencil 第二代的新产品，而是入门版本。<br /><span id="more-1199849"></span></p><p>今次推出的 Apple Pencil (USB-C) 顾名思义，采用了现在成为标准规格的 USB-C 插口作充电，不再支援无线充电，此外虽然基本功能不变，但原先第二代 Apple Pencil 的一些高阶功能例如压力感应、按两下切换工具都欠奉，购买时也不能免费镭射刻名，不过价格方面就比现有第二代 Apple Pencil（HK$999）甚至第一代 Apple Pencil（HK$779）都便宜，只需 HK$619。</p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg" alt="" width="1960" height="1102" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1199851" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-USB-C-sliding-cap_big.jpg.large_2x-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>Apple Pencil (USB-C) 支援所有配备 USB-C 接口的 iPad 型号，尤其是之前只可以使用第一代 Apple Pencil（不过要使用 USB-C 至 Apple Pencil 转换器来配对或充电）的第 10 代 iPad 就可以完美配合新的 Apple Pencil (USB-C)。它将会在 11 月初正式发售，不过实际日期并未公布。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg" alt="" width="1960" height="2308" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1199852" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x-493x580.jpg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x-764x900.jpg 764w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x-768x904.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Pencil-features-comparison_big.jpg.large_2x-1304x1536.jpg 1304w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2023/10/apple-introduces-new-apple-pencil-bringing-more-value-and-choice-to-the-lineup/">Apple</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
